ProductName: Califia Farms® Organic Unsweetened Almondmilk
ProductSubCategory: Califia Farms® Organic Unsweetened Almondmilk
Description:
Organic Almondmilk–pure and simple. We expertly blend just water, almonds and sea salt to create this dairy-free deliciousness in its purest plant-based form. No oils and no gums. All organic with zero additives. By itself, it’s a smooth drink to be savored. In cereal and smoothies, it elevates the flavor profile with the slight sweetness of organic almonds. In recipes, it makes the perfect ingredient replacement any time dairy milk is used. This Organic Almondmilk will settle naturally demonstrating its wholesomeness. Shake before using and recall all its organic virtues: just three simple ingredients and totally free from dairy, oil, gums, gluten, soy, and carrageenan.
NO OILS, NO GUMS: Califia® Organic Almondmilk is made with just three simple ingredients without the need for oils or gums. Just shake it up and enjoy
CERTIFIED USDA ORGANIC: Califia® Organic Almondmilk is USDA certified organic with zero additives. No dairy, oil, gums, gluten, soy, and carrageenan. It’s everything you want in dairy-free almond milk and nothing you don’t
THREE SIMPLE INGREDIENTS: Purified water, organic almonds, and sea salt. This is plant-based dairy-free goodness in its purest form. No oils and no gums. It’s deliciously simple
DELICIOUS HOMEMADE TASTE: Califia® Farms Organic Almondmilk delivers true homemade taste with organic almonds combined with purified water and sea salt. All the rich smoothness you desire without a trace of dairy
SHAKE, POUR, LOVE: Settling is natural in high-quality plant-based milks so remember to shake well! Then enjoy the rich, creamy taste created by three simple ingredients

Description:
Just three simple ingredients come together to create Califia Farms® Organic Almondmilk: water, almonds and sea salt. No oils, no gums. This is plant-based, dairy-free goodness in its purest form. All organic. Zero additives. Free from dairy, oil, gums, gluten, soy, and carrageenan. Settling is natural for a almond milk that’s this pure and simple, so shake it before you enjoy it.
NO OILS, NO GUMS: Califia Organic Almondmilk is made with just three simple ingredients without the need for oils or gums. Just shake it up and enjoy!
CERTIFIED USDA ORGANIC: Califia Organic Almondmilk is USDA certified organic with zero additives. No dairy, oil, gums, gluten, soy, and carrageenan. It’s everything you want in dairy-free almond milk and nothing you don’t.
THREE SIMPLE INGREDIENTS: Purified water, organic almonds, and sea salt. This is plant-based dairy-free goodness in its purest form. No oils and no gums. It’s deliciously simple.
DELICIOUS HOMEMADE TASTE: Califia Farms® Organic Almondmilk delivers true homemade taste with organic almonds combined with purified water and sea salt. All the rich smoothness you desire without a trace of dairy.
SHAKE, POUR, LOVE: Settling is natural in high-quality plant-based milks so remember to shake well! Then enjoy the rich, creamy taste created by three simple ingredients.

ProductName: Califia Farms® Organic Oatmilk

Description:
Organic Oatmilk pure and simple. We expertly blend just water, oats and sea salt to create this dairy-free deliciousness in its purest plant-based form. No oils and no gums. All organic with zero additives. By itself, it’s a creamy drink to be savored. In coffees and smoothies, it elevates the flavor profile with the slight sweetness of organic oats. In recipes, it makes the perfect ingredient replacement any time dairy milk is used. This Organic Oatmilk will settle naturally demonstrating its wholesomeness. Shake before using and recall all its organic virtues: just three simple ingredients and totally free from dairy, oil, gums, nuts, soy, and carrageenan.
NO OILS, NO GUMS: Califia Organic Oatmilk is made with just three simple ingredients without oils or gums. Just shake it up and enjoy!
CERTIFIED USDA ORGANIC: Califia Organic Oatmilk is USDA certified organic with zero additives. No dairy, oil, gums, nuts, soy, and carrageenan. It’s everything you want in dairy-free plant milk and nothing you don’t.
THREE SIMPLE INGREDIENTS: Purified water, organic oats, and sea salt. This is plant-based dairy-free goodness in its purest form. No oils and no gums. It’s deliciously simple.
PLANT-BASED: Califia Farms® products are made with plant-based ingredients to acheive irresistible goodness in every way––taste, versatility, and all the benefits of being dairy-free.
DON'T FORGET TO SHAKE: Settling is natural in high-quality plant-based milks so remember to shake well!

ProductName: Prairie Farms Dairy Fresh 2% Milk
ProductSubCategory: Prairie Farms Dairy Fresh 2% Milk
Description:
Prairie Farms Shelf Stable 2% Reduced Fat Milk is a refreshing and delicious nutrient powerhouse that requires no refrigeration, so it can be easily stored in your pantry until ready to use. Just refrigerate before using to chill, then enjoy over cereal or with your favorite snack. Each 1 cup serving is packed with nine essential nutrients, including 8 grams of high-quality protein, calcium, Vitamins A & D, niacin, riboflavin, potassium, and phosphorus. Prairie Farms Shelf Stable 2% Reduced Fat Milk is also perfect for baking and cooking.

Before leaving our family farms, Prairie Farms milk goes through strict quality control measures to guarantee freshness and is always free from artificial growth hormones and antibiotics. Within 24 hours, the milk is delivered to one of our farmer-owned facilities for production and packaging into a wide variety of high-quality dairy products. This process sets Prairie Farms Shelf Stable 2% Reduced Fat Milk apart because we are 100% in control of the farm-to-table cycle.

Did you know each time you buy Prairie Farms Shelf Stable 2% Reduced Fat Milk you are supporting local dairy farm families? Visit one of our farms on any given day, and you’ll find family members pitching in. We love our cows, and you’ll find them relaxing in a barn or grazing in a pasture. They always have access to plenty of clean water and food – often they eat before we do! Prairie Farms’ Animal Care Program, F.A.R.M., is recognized by the International Organization for Standardization (ISO) for its industry-leading animal care standards.

Whether it’s caring for our cows or caring for the land using sustainable farming practices, producing the highest quality Shelf Stable 2% Reduced Fat Milk and naturally good dairy products has been the Prairie Farms way since 1938. Dedicated Farmers | Happy Cows | Real Milk | PrairieFarms.com
Easy Storage. No Refrigeration Required. No artificial Growth Hormones

ProductName: Truvia Natural Sweetener, 400 Count (Pack of 1)
ProductSubCategory: Truvia Natural Sweetener, 400 Count (Pack of 1)
Description: Sweetness is meant to be enjoyed. That's why Truvia created products meant to reduce sugar, not taste. The clean, sweet flavor contained in Truvia Natural Sweetener packets comes from nature in the form of the stevia leaf. Leaves don't dissolve well in beverages or baked goods, so we extract the sweetness from the stevia leaf. Because stevia leaf extract is 200x sweeter than sugar, we balance the sweetness with erythritol, a sweetener produced by fermentation. Erythritol is also found in fruits like grapes and pears. This gives you the white crystals you're used to without the calories. This 400-count box can be stashed at home, at work or a few packets can be thrown in your bag for on-the-go sweetness.
